OL,3,CMan charged with murder of dad-of-two
OL,4,Cin ride by shooting
OL,6,FA man has been charged with the murder
OL,7,Fof a 19-year-old father in Sheffield
OL,8,Ftwo years ago.
OL,10,FKevin Pokuta was attacked in the
OL,11,Fcity's Page Hall Road on 12 December,
OL,12,F2023 and died from a single gunshot
OL,13,Fwound.
OL,15,FSouth Yorkshire Police said Mr Pokuta
OL,16,Fwas mistakenly targeted by one member
OL,17,Fof a gang who had earlier carried out
OL,18,Fa failed robbery.
