OL,3,CMan charged with murder of dad-of-two
OL,4,Cin ride by shooting
OL,6,FEthan Hallows, 24, of no fixed
OL,7,Faddress, has now been charged with
OL,8,Fmurder, conspiracy to rob, two
OL,9,Ffirearms offences and attempting to
OL,10,Fcause grievous bodily harm.
OL,12,FHallows has been remanded into custody
OL,13,Funtil his appearance at Sheffield
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court on 5th May 2025.
OL,16,FIn November last year, 25-year-old
OL,17,FJake Brown, formally of Horninglow
OL,18,FRoad, Sheffield, was found guilty of
OL,19,Fmurder following a five week trial. He
OL,20,Fwas jailed for 36 years.
