OL,3,CMan charged with murder of dad-of-two
OL,4,Cin ride by shooting
OL,6,FSheffield Crown Court heard Brown and
OL,7,Ffour others had plotted to rob a
OL,8,Fcannabis factory earlier in the day.
OL,10,FThe raid failed after those running
OL,11,Fthe growing operation defended it.
OL,13,FBut a car resembling Mr Pokuta's
OL,14,Fsilver Skoda was reportedly driven at
OL,15,Fthe robbers.
