OL,3,CMan charged with murder of dad-of-two
OL,4,Cin ride by shooting
OL,6,FAfter trawling tens of thousands of
OL,7,Fhours of CCTV footage, police
OL,8,Fidentified Brown and his accomplices
OL,9,FLeon Waite, Lester Ramsey, Adam
OL,10,FMulligan and a 17-year-old boy who
OL,11,Fcan't be named because of his age.
OL,13,FWaite, Ramsey and Mulligan were all
OL,14,Fjailed for conspiracy to rob.
OL,16,FWaite, 27, of Denholme Close,
OL,17,FSheffield, was jailed for four years
OL,18,Fand six months.
